  "text": "utilize the technique outlined in [CITATION_1] . However, we determined that small errors in estimates of each debris tag's size or distance resulted in large errors in the calculated wind speed. Therefore, estimates of debris-derived tornadic wind speeds using photogrammetry are not provided in this paper. These limitations emphasize the utility of deploying two video probes in future deployments for stereo photogrammetric analysis.",
